messages.message:
Hi Team,

I have a client is asking if the *SDLC* is going to be being replaced by anything?

they have noticed the

"The Instabase SDLC feature is in long-term support (LTS). We will fix any critical bugs, but there will not be any further feature development. (https://instabase.com/docs/platform-admin/sdlc/index.html)"

:smiley: Hi @Heymian

I found a previous chat about this, but it was a year ago. I just want to ensure that it's still valid. (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C06FA6A23/p1658247484486929?thread_ts=1658246642.321719&cid=C06FA6A23)
Yes, that is still valid. There are no plans to replace it with anything.
